                               </tr>
                           </table>

                           <table class="table table-bordered">
                               <tr>
                                   <th colspan="1">
                                       3.) Date of Disclosure of the APAR to the officer reported upon
                                   </th>
                                   <th colspan="2">
                                       <span t-field="o.create_date"/>
                                   </th>
                               </tr>
                           </table>

                           <p>
                               I have read all entries of my APAR for the year/period <span t-field="o.abap_period"/>
